<manpage>
    <volume> 常用数据结构 </volume>
    <interface> MemoryBuf</interface>

    <description>       
        <para>MemoryBuf继承自BufferOf。操作对象是字节的内存块。</para>
        <para>MemoryBuf构造函数和各种方法使用介绍：</para>
        <para>以下只列出比BufferOf多的方法，相同或相似的方法请参考BufferOf</para>
        <para>操作符与BufferOf相同</para>
   </description>
    <constructs>
        <construct>
            <construct_name>MemoryBuf_(Int32 SIZE )</construct_name>
            <construct_url>MemoryBuf/structure/MemoryBuf1</construct_url>
            <construct_description>在栈中构造一个MemoryBuf对象,包括SIZE字节的buffer内存空间 </construct_description>
        </construct>
        
        <construct>
            <construct_name>MemoryBuf(T *pBuf, Int32 capacity, Int32 used)</construct_name>
            <construct_url>MemoryBuf/structure/MemoryBuf2</construct_url>
            <construct_description>在栈中构造一个MemoryBuf对象,将m_pBuf指向用户指定的内存块，并分别其长度和已使用长度.</construct_description>
        </construct>
        
        <construct>
            <construct_name>MemoryBuf( T *pBuf, Int32 capacity)</construct_name>
            <construct_url>MemoryBuf/structure/MemoryBuf3</construct_url>
            <construct_description>在栈中构造一个MemoryBuf对象,将m_pBuf指向用户指定的内存块，并分别其长度和已使用长度为capacity</construct_description>
        </construct>
     </constructs>   
        
    <methods>
      <self>
        <method>
        <method_name>SetByteVaule</method_name>
        <method_url>MemoryBuf/SetByteVaule</method_url>
        <m_description>设置内存块的字节值，相当于memset  </m_description>
        </method>
        
        <method>
        <method_name> Compare(const Byte* pBuf, Int32 n)</method_name>
        <method_url>MemoryBuf/Compare1</method_url>
        <m_description> 与指定内存块比较n个字节，相当于memcmp </m_description>
        </method>
        
        <method>
        <method_name>Compare(const PCarQuintet pCq)</method_name>
        <method_url>MemoryBuf/Compare</method_url>
        <m_description> 与的指定五元组的数据区比较目标五元组的used个字节</m_description>
        </method>
        
      </self>
    </methods>


   
    <macros>
        <macro>
        <macro_name> NULL_MEMORYBUF&lt;T&gt;  </macro_name>
         <macro_url> MemoryBuf/NULL_MEMORYBUF  </macro_url>
        <macro_description> 构造一个内容为空的MemoryBuf对象  </macro_description>
        </macro>
        <macro>
        <macro_name> AUTO_MEMORYBUF(n)  </macro_name>
         <macro_url> MemoryBuf/AUTO_MEMORYBUF  </macro_url>
        <macro_description> 构造一个大小为n的MemoryBuf对象  </macro_description>
        </macro>
    </macros>    
        
        
</manpage>     
        
        
       
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
    

    